  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK565">
<l>aruñcevvi yiṉṉā mukattāṉ peruñcelvam </l>
<l>pēykaṇṭa taṉṉa tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great wealth of him who is difficult of access and possesses a sternness of countenance, is like that which has been obtained by a devil.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
